npm i --save bootstrap

How to use bootsrap in React Application?

Step1 : Add HTML Element to Form  <input type="text" />
Step2:  Add new state property and assign the component state to element value
    this.state = {
        userName:''   
    }
    and assign state to element value 
    <input type="text"  value={this.state.userName} />
   Narasim

step3: assign the event handler, for to update state. 
<input type="text"  value={this.state.userName} onChange={this.changeUserName}/>